'''肝功能測試'''（{{lang-en|Liver function tests}}）是為了解病患[[肝臟|肝臟]]的狀態，設計而成的[[化學病理學|臨床生化學]]實驗室血液檢測方法的總稱<ref name="Lee2009">{{cite book|last=Lee|first=Mary|title=Basic Skills in Interpreting Laboratory Data|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=AUSIRcV_as0C&pg=PA259|accessdate=2011-08-05|date=2009-03-10|publisher=ASHP|isbn=9781585281800|pages=259–|language=en}}</ref>。相關測試參數包括：PT/INR（[[凝血酶原時間|凝血酶原時間]]／[[凝血酶原時間|國際標準化比值]]）、aPTT、[[白蛋白|白蛋白]]、[[膽紅素|膽紅素]]（直接和間接）、[[谷丙转氨酶|谷丙转氨酶]]等。<ref name="pmid10221307">{{cite journal | author = Johnston DE | title = Special considerations in interpreting liver function tests | journal = Am Fam Physician | volume = 59 | issue = 8 | pages = 2223–30 | year = 1999 | pmid = 10221307 | doi =  }}</ref><ref name="McClatchey2002">{{cite book|last=McClatchey|first=Kenneth D.|title=Clinical laboratory medicine|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=3PJVLH1NmQAC&pg=PA288|accessdate=5 August 2011|year=2002|publisher=Lippincott Williams & Wilkins|isbn=978-0-683-30751-1|pages=288–}}</ref><ref name="MengelSchwiebert2005">{{cite book|last1=Mengel|first1=Mark B.|last2=Schwiebert|first2=L. Peter|title=Family medicine: ambulatory care & prevention|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=XvLo7xvmFo0C&pg=PA268|accessdate=5 August 2011|year=2005|publisher=McGraw-Hill Professional|isbn=978-0-07-142322-9|pages=268–}}</ref>

